These VEP scripts were retired because others were created that are easier to use and interpret.
Note, that when this script was run 'splice_donor_variant' that are LC were assigned to 'pLoF' consequence. This
will not affect results when pLoF+damaging missense are already run together. This issue is super rare and affects
only a few variants on each chromsome (chr20 has 2, chr21 has 1.. etc).




